        "textContents": [
          {
            "pos": 1,
            "template": "plain",
            "body": "<p>Welcome to the city tour about the his­tory of the FSV Frankfurt and Born­hei­mer bars.</p>\n<p>The city tour was created by the his­tory group of the FSV Frankfurt fan and sup­port department (deutsch: Fan- und Förder­ab­tei­lung). We wish you a good time.</p>",
